<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.7.10">
<l>malipukaḻ kaṇapura muṭaiyave maṭikaḷai</l>
<l>valikeḻu matiḷayal vayalaṇi maṅkaiyar</l>
<l>kaliyaṉa tamiḻivai viḻumiya vicaiyiṉo</l>
<l>ṭolicolu maṭiyava ruṟutuya rilarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those devotees who say the words of these Tamil [verses] with sublime music</l>
<l>Of Kaliyaṉ of those of lovely Maṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">with fields adjacent to strong thick walls,</l>
<l>About our god who belongs to Kaṇṇapuram with increasing fame,</l>
<l rend="indent">They will not suffer sorrows.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
